Looks like you have an incorrect `LD_LIBRARY_PATH`. Try to set the following values:
```
export PATH=/usr/local/cuda-9.0/bin:${PATH}
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/cuda-9.0/lib64${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:+:${LD_LIBRARY_PATH}}
```
